# Part 1 - Observability Architecture

## Purpose

Observability enables engineers to understand

- System Behaviour
- Business Behaviour
- Platform Health
- Customer Experience
- AI Behaviour
- Distributed Workflows

Observability is designed into the platform.

It is never added after deployment.

